 <span data-ttu-id="1b824-105">如果您指定`Auto`如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.ScrollBars%2A>屬性，自動捲軸時中內容的大小<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>控制項的大小超過<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b824-105">If you specify `Auto` for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.ScrollBars%2A> property, scroll bars are automatically shown when the size of the content in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control exceeds the size of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b824-106">例如，如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>控制項包含一個資料表，以及面板不寬度不足以顯示資料表中的所有資料列，顯示垂直捲軸。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b824-106">For example, if a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control contains a table, and the panel is not wide enough to display all the rows in the table, a vertical scroll bar is shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b824-107">如果資料表的大小超過面板的寬度與高度，顯示垂直和水平捲軸。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b824-107">If the size of the table exceeds the height and width of the panel, both vertical and horizontal scroll bars are shown.</span></span>  
  
   
  
